Class TGBaseTurnByTurnFragment

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TGTurnByTurnFragment

    public abstract class TGBaseTurnByTurnFragment
extends TGBaseMapFragment
    An implementation of TGBaseMapFragment that allows for easy interaction with the TGNavigationService navigation. This Fragment can be used in conjunction with TGMapFragment to create a fully functional navigation and search application.
